TA to Postsecondary Institutions
Designed for postsecondary institutions from state teams interested
in scaling their own ATB usage will receive support from subject
matter experts and project advisors and engage in peer learning and
sharing opportunities 
25
TA Objectives (2)
TA will help postsecondary institutions achieve the following
objectives:
• Increase awareness of successful models of ATB usage
• Integrate ATB usage into their integrated education and training
(IET) programs and career pathway initiatives
• Utilize promising practices and challenge
• Leverage their state-defined process to increase usage of all ATB
methods
• Complete the ECPP approval process
